        "content": "<p>This way, you get to \"label\" each expression. And it doesn't count as shadowing because field names don't clash with variable names. And yet the record destructuring syntax makes them the same names. <span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span></p>",
